Insider Activity


Individual




David C. Habiger



Mr. David C. Habiger is Independent Director at Enova International, Inc., Independent Director at Immersion Corp., Independent Director at DTS, Inc., Independent Director at Echo Global Logistics, Inc., Chief Executive Officer & Director at Textura Corp., Lead Independent Director at Control4 Corp., Independent Director at RealD, Inc., a Member at The National Association of Corporate Directors, Inc., a Member at Center for Corporate Innovation, Chief Executive Officer & Director at NDS Group Holdings Ltd., and Venture Partner at The Pritzker Group. He is on the Board of Directors at Enova International, Inc., Immersion Corp., DTS, Inc., Echo Global Logistics, Inc., Textura Corp., Control4 Corp., RealD, Inc., Silicon Valley Leadership Group, The Next New You, NDS Group Holdings Ltd., LiquidPiston, Inc., and QuickPlay Media, Inc.
Mr. Habiger was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer & Director by NDS Group Ltd., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Sonic Solutions LLC, Founder by Providence Productions, and an Product Manager by Roscor Corp. He also served on the board at Akimbo Systems, Inc. and Hinsdale Historical Society.
He received his undergraduate degree from St. Norbert College, Inc. and an MBA from The University of Chicago.



